      "span_text": "The cDNA library was sequenced on the Illumina sequencing platform (GAII). The raw reads from the images were generated using Solexa GA pipeline 1.6. After removal of low quality reads, processed reads with an identity value of 95% and a coverage length of 100 bp were assembled using SOAP denovo software and clustered using TGI Clustering tools [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ."
